<h3>Why won't my LG dryer start even though it has power?</h3>
<p>The most common cause is a blown thermal fuse, which cuts power to the motor when the dryer overheats from restricted airflow. Door latch problems and faulty start switches are also frequent culprits. Professional diagnosis determines the exact cause and prevents misdiagnosis.</p>
